attributes.description: The Dashboard provides a comprehensive analysis of Amazon shirt listings, focusing on key metrics such as total unique products, average discount percentage, and customer ratings. It visualizes trends in discount distribution and highlights the top-rated shirts based on median customer ratings. The dashboard also includes tables displaying shirt names, images, and key performance metrics, helping in product comparison. By analyzing discounts, ratings, and product counts, this dashboard offers valuable insights for understanding customer preferences, optimizing pricing strategies, and improving sales performance.
